fix: resolve build errors and CI runner deprecation

- CloudflareTunnel.swift: rewrite with auto-download (was reverted by merge)
  - Remove .notInstalled status, use .downloading for auto-download flow
  - Mark supportDir/binaryPath as nonisolated to fix actor isolation error
- SettingsView.swift: replace .notInstalled references with .downloading UI
  - Fix tunnel button color (amber -> theme.accent)
  - Use .isBusy for disabled state instead of .starting only
- CI: replace deprecated macos-13 runner with macos-14 cross-compilation
  - build.sh: support ARCH env var for --arch cross-compile
  - create-dmg.sh: use ARCH env var for DMG filename
  - release.yml: single macos-14 runner with matrix arch
  - Add xattr fix instructions to release notes
- PLAN.md: update TunnelStatus enum, document CI changes
